=== ANCIENT_TERMINAL ===
# id: 0
# title: Ancient Terminal
# chinese_title: 古代终端
# category: Terminal
# mode: dungeon

A flickering holographic terminal protrudes from the wall. Faded Chinese characters scroll across its surface, hinting at forgotten knowledge.

* [Attempt to read the characters] {requires: radical == "言"}
  ~ gain_xp(20)
  阅读 (yuèdú) — read
* [Smash the terminal for parts]
  ~ gain_gold(5)
  破坏 (pòhuài) — destroy
* [Leave it alone]
  ~ nothing
  忽视 (hūshì) — ignore
